{"serial": "11015", "department_serial": 10, "code": "CL0201", "class": "A", "name": {"en": "Chinese (B): Chinese writing", "ch": "國文（B）：中文寫作"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": "劉德明、李欣倫"}, "instructor": {"en": ["Liu, Te-Ming", "Li,Xin-Lun"], "ch": ["劉德明", "李欣倫"]}, "credits": 2, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "A", "room": "109"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 29, "department": {"ch": "中國文學系", "en": "Department of Chinese Literature"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 6, "selected": 29, "remark": {"ch": "劉德明、李欣倫", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "論文寫作部分：讓學生了解論文寫作的目的，並實際操作及了解如何撰寫出學術論文。【創意寫作】的部分：本課程將介紹台灣當代文學常見的文類，也是台灣各大文學獎常見的文類概說及作品閱讀，包括現代詩、當代散文、當代小說和報導文學等，期盼能透過每週閱讀、分析作品，掌握基礎寫作技巧，實際帶領同學練習各文類的初階寫作。", "en": "The thesis writing section: Students will understand the purpose of thesis writing and learn how to write an academic thesis in a practical way.\nThe Creative Writing: This course will introduce the common genres of contemporary literature in Taiwan, as well as an overview of the genres commonly awarded by the Taiwan Literature Prize and the reading of their works, including modern poetry, contemporary prose, contemporary fiction, and reportage literature, etc. The hope is that through reading and analyzing the works each week, we can master the basic skills of writing, and practically lead the students to practice the beginning writing of each genre."}, "outline": {"ch": "論文寫作部分：\n1.如何擬定題目\n2,如何撰寫摘要及關鍵詞\n3.如何搜集相關資料\n4.論文格式\n5.前言與結論\n【創意寫作】\n1.現代詩簡介\n2.當代散文簡介\n3.當代小說簡介\n4.報導文學簡介", "en": "Essay Writing Section.\n1. How to write a topic\n2. How to write the abstract and key words\n3. How to collect relevant information\n4. Format of thesis\n5. Preface and conclusion\nCreative Writing：\n1.Contemporary Poetry Writing\n2.Essays writing\n3.Fiction Writing\n4.Non-Fiction Writing"}, "textbook": {"ch": "教科書：自編講義\n參考書：林慶彰《學術論文寫作指引》，萬卷樓圖書有限公司，1996年", "en": "Self-Editing Handouts"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "100%", "en": "100%"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授", "en": ["Lecture"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "論文寫作部分：佔50分\n平常出勤及參與討論情況： 20％\n作業：80％\n\n創意寫作部分：\n課堂發言：20％\n\n課堂寫作：80％", "en": "Essay Writing Section:  50 points\nUsual attendance and participation in discussions: 20％\nAssignments: 80％\n\nCreative Writing:50 points\nGroup discussions: 20％\nWriting: 80％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "星期二 5、6 星期三 5、6  星期四 2", "en": "Tuesday 5, 6 Wednesday 5, 6 Thursday 2"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "17+1", "en": "17+1"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "重新修訂論文寫作各部份的平時作業\n創作部分：作品討論", "en": "Revise the usual assignments for each part of the essay writing"}, "domain": {"ch": "應用中文", "en": "應用中文"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "文獻解讀", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "邏輯思辨", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "語文表達", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "文學鑑賞", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["作業練習", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "人文素養與國際視野", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["作業練習", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Interpreting classics", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Practices/Experiments", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Logical thinking", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Practices/Experiments", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Language communication", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Practices/Experiments", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Appreciation of literature", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Practices/Experiments", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Humanistic and international outlook", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Practices/Experiments", "Attendance/Performan